---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="ブログ｜発酵・ローフード・リビングフードの知恵と実践 | &LAB TOKYO"
  canonical="https://www.andlabtokyo.com/blog"
>

<style>
*,*::before,*::after{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
    
    
    .page-header{margin-top:44px;padding:64px 22px 48px;background:var(--bg-2);text-align:center;border-bottom:1px solid var(--divider);}
    .header-eye{font-family:var(--fh);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:4px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--green-d);display:block;margin-bottom:12px;}
    .page-header h1{font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,44px);font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:12px;}
    .page-header p{font-size:15px;color:var(--ink-3);max-width:480px;margin:0 auto;}
    .categories{padding:20px 22px;background:var(--bg);border-bottom:1px solid var(--divider);position:sticky;top:44px;z-index:50;}
    .cat-inner{max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
    .cat-btn{font-size:13px;font-weight:500;padding:7px 16px;border-radius:980px;text-decoration:none;transition:all .2s;border:1.5px solid var(--divider);color:var(--ink-3);}
    .cat-btn:hover,.cat-btn.active{background:var(--green);color:#1d1d1f;border-color:var(--green);}
    .featured{padding:48px 22px 0;background:var(--bg);}
    .featured-inner{max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto;}
    .featured-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:3px;}
    .featured-main{position:relative;overflow:hidden;height:440px;text-decoration:none;display:block;}
    .featured-main img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;transition:transform .7s;}
    .featured-main:hover img{transform:scale(1.03);}
    .featured-main::after{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(0,0,0,.78) 0%,rgba(0,0,0,.1) 55%,transparent 100%);}
    .feat-cat{font-family:var(--fh);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--green);margin-bottom:8px;display:block;}
    .featured-main h2{font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;line-height:1.4;margin-bottom:8px;}
    .feat-date{font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.55);}
    .featured-sub{display:grid;grid-template-rows:1fr 1fr;gap:3px;}
    .feat-sub-card{position:relative;overflow:hidden;height:216px;text-decoration:none;display:block;}
    .feat-sub-card img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;transition:transform .7s;}
    .feat-sub-card:hover img{transform:scale(1.04);}
    .feat-sub-card::after{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(0,0,0,.75) 0%,transparent 60%);}
    .feat-sub-body span{font-family:var(--fh);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--green);display:block;margin-bottom:4px;}
    .feat-sub-body h3{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;line-height:1.4;}
    .articles{padding:48px 22px 72px;background:var(--bg);}
    .articles-inner{max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto;}
    .articles-label{font-family:var(--fh);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:4px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-3);display:block;margin-bottom:28px;}
    .article-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1px;background:var(--divider);}
    .article-card{background:var(--bg);text-decoration:none;display:block;transition:background .2s;}
    .article-card:hover{background:var(--bg-2);}
    .article-card-img{width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/10;object-fit:cover;display:block;}
    .article-cat{font-family:var(--fh);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--green-d);display:block;margin-bottom:6px;}
    .article-card h3{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:8px;}
    .article-card p{font-size:13px;color:var(--ink-3);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:12px;}
    .article-date{font-size:12px;color:var(--divider);}
    .knowledge{padding:56px 22px;background:var(--bg-2);}
    .knowledge-inner{max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto;}
    .knowledge-eye{font-family:var(--fh);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:4px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--green-d);display:block;margin-bottom:10px;}
    .knowledge h2{font-size:clamp(22px,3vw,32px);font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:8px;}
    .knowledge-sub{font-size:15px;color:var(--ink-3);margin-bottom:36px;}
    .knowledge-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:2px;}
    .knowledge-card{background:var(--bg);padding:24px 20px;text-decoration:none;display:block;border-bottom:2px solid transparent;transition:border-color .2s,background .2s;}
    .knowledge-card:hover{border-bottom-color:var(--green);background:var(--bg-2);}
    .knowledge-card-icon{font-size:24px;margin-bottom:12px;display:block;}
    .knowledge-card h4{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:6px;}
    .knowledge-card p{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-3);line-height:1.7;}
    .note-sec{padding:48px 22px;background:var(--bg-dark);text-align:center;}
    .note-eye{font-family:var(--fh);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:4px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--green);display:block;margin-bottom:12px;}
    .note-sec h2{font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,30px);font-weight:700;color:#f5f5f7;margin-bottom:12px;}
    .note-sec p{font-size:15px;color:rgba(245,245,247,.6);margin-bottom:24px;}
    .btn-note{display:inline-block;border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.35);color:rgba(255,255,255,.85);font-size:14px;padding:12px 28px;border-radius:980px;text-decoration:none;transition:all .2s;}
    .btn-note:hover{border-color:#fff;color:#fff;}
    
    
    @media(max-width:768px){.featured-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}.article-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}.knowledge-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}}
</style>

<div class="page-header">
    <span class="header-eye">Journal</span>
    <h1>食と発酵の、知恵と実践。</h1>
    <p>ローフード・発酵・リビングフード・ロースイーツについて。細胞から整える食の知恵を発信します。</p>
  </div>
  <div class="categories">
    <div class="cat-inner">
      <a href="/blog" class="cat-btn active">すべて</a>
      <a href="/rawfood" class="cat-btn">ローフード</a>
      <a href="/fermentation" class="cat-btn">発酵</a>
      <a href="/living-food" class="cat-btn">リビングフード</a>
      <a href="/raw-sweets" class="cat-btn">ロースイーツ</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <section class="featured">
    <div class="featured-inner">
      <div class="featured-grid">
        <a href="/rawfood" class="featured-main">
          <img src="/rawfood-zucchini.jpg" alt="ローフード" />
          <div class="featured-main-body">
            <span class="feat-cat">Raw Food</span>
            <h2>酵素を壊さない調理の5つの基本。なぜ48℃なのか</h2>
            <p class="feat-date">2026.05.20</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <div class="featured-sub">
          <a href="/fermentation" class="feat-sub-card">
            <img src="/hacco-amazake.jpg" alt="発酵" />
            <div class="feat-sub-body">
              <span>Fermentation</span>
              <h3>自家製麹の作り方。初心者でも失敗しないポイント</h3>
            </div>
          </a>
          <a href="/living-food" class="feat-sub-card">
            <img src="/visual-table.jpg" alt="リビングフード" />
            <div class="feat-sub-body">
              <span>Living Food</span>
              <h3>40代から始める「細胞から整える」ローフード習慣</h3>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="articles">
    <div class="articles-inner">
      <span class="articles-label">Recent Articles</span>
      <div class="article-grid">
        <a href="/fermentation" class="article-card">
          <img src="/koji.jpg" alt="麹" class="article-card-img" />
          <div class="article-card-body">
            <span class="article-cat">Fermentation</span>
            <h3>麹とは何か。甘麹・塩麹・醤油麹の違いと使い方</h3>
            <p>日本古来の発酵文化、麹の基礎知識を解説します。</p>
            <span class="article-date">2026.05.15</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/raw-sweets" class="article-card">
          <img src="/prog-chocolate.jpg" alt="ローチョコ" class="article-card-img" />
          <div class="article-card-body">
            <span class="article-cat">Raw Sweets</span>
            <h3>ローチョコレートがなぜ体に良いのか。カカオの科学</h3>
            <p>カカオポリフェノールとマグネシウムの働きを解説。</p>
            <span class="article-date">2026.05.08</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/about" class="article-card">
          <img src="/story-lesson.jpg" alt="レッスン" class="article-card-img" />
          <div class="article-card-body">
            <span class="article-cat">Story</span>
            <h3>娘の大火傷が、私を食の世界へ導いた。安藤千英の原点</h3>
            <p>&LAB TOKYOが生まれるまでのストーリー。</p>
            <span class="article-date">2026.04.28</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/rawfood" class="article-card">
          <img src="/green-smoothie.jpg" alt="スムージー" class="article-card-img" />
          <div class="article-card-body">
            <span class="article-cat">Raw Food</span>
            <h3>毎朝のグリーンスムージーで変わる、細胞からの体質改善</h3>
            <p>忙しい朝でも続けられる、酵素スムージーの作り方。</p>
            <span class="article-date">2026.04.20</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/fermentation" class="article-card">
          <img src="/hacco-koji.jpg" alt="麹素材" class="article-card-img" />
          <div class="article-card-body">
            <span class="article-cat">Fermentation</span>
            <h3>腸内環境と美肌の関係。発酵食が肌に効く理由</h3>
            <p>腸は「第二の脳」であり「美肌の鍵」。科学的に解説。</p>
            <span class="article-date">2026.04.10</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/living-food" class="article-card">
          <img src="/brand-sushi.jpg" alt="リビングフード" class="article-card-img" />
          <div class="article-card-body">
            <span class="article-cat">Living Food</span>
            <h3>忙しい経営者・専門職が「食で自分を整える」方法</h3>
            <p>パフォーマンスを上げる食習慣。リビングフードの実践。</p>
            <span class="article-date">2026.03.28</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="knowledge">
    <div class="knowledge-inner">
      <span class="knowledge-eye">Knowledge Hub</span>
      <h2>テーマ別に学ぶ</h2>
      <p class="knowledge-sub">各テーマの基礎知識からレッスン情報まで</p>
      <div class="knowledge-grid">
        <a href="/rawfood" class="knowledge-card"><span class="knowledge-card-icon">🌿</span><h4>ローフード</h4><p>酵素・栄養・48℃の科学。生食の基礎から実践まで。</p></a>
        <a href="/fermentation" class="knowledge-card"><span class="knowledge-card-icon">🍶</span><h4>発酵</h4><p>麹・味噌・醤油。日本の発酵文化と腸内環境の知識。</p></a>
        <a href="/living-food" class="knowledge-card"><span class="knowledge-card-icon">✨</span><h4>リビングフード</h4><p>発酵×ローフードのクロス理論。細胞から整えるライフスタイル。</p></a>
        <a href="/raw-sweets" class="knowledge-card"><span class="knowledge-card-icon">🍫</span><h4>ロースイーツ</h4><p>砂糖不使用の美しいお菓子。カカオの科学と実践。</p></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="note-sec">
    <span class="note-eye">Note</span>
    <h2>安藤千英のnoteも読む</h2>
    <p>より深いストーリーや日々の実践を、noteで綴っています。</p>
    <a href="https://note.com/chieando" target="_blank" class="btn-note">noteを読む →</a>
  </section>

</Layout>
